to read this and give me feedback.

01:50.027 --> 01:51.061
Joel...

01:52.362 --> 01:53.320
the Orgy Guy ?

01:53.488 --> 01:56.991
Can we call him Joel the guy who is
going to help Casey get into Law School?

01:57.311 --> 02:00.358
