world has motivated me

07:21.840 --> 07:24.222
- to do the same.
- To boldly go where

07:24.347 --> 07:26.361
ten percent of men have gone before.

07:27.679 --> 07:30.152
Yeah. Seriously.
Stop dancing.

07:30.277 --> 07:33.087
Evan, I was looking for you.
I was going through the receipts from

07:33.212 --> 07:36.663
