write for mine, either.

10:02.978 --> 10:05.854
- How'd you figure it out ?
- The Backstreet Boys.

10:06.022 --> 10:07.481
I can write about them.

10:07.650 --> 10:09.149
It wasn't just about them.

10:09.318 --> 10:12.792
I couldn't understand how the Supreme
Court had made such a bad decision

10:12.917 --> 10:14.800
